				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the abbreviation, see <a href="VC_(disambiguation)" title="VC (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">VC</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="Victoria_Cross_(disambiguation)" title="Victoria Cross (disambiguation)">Victoria Cross (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
