<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;">Level 1</div>
</th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Victoria_Cross_(Canada)_ribbon_bar.png" class="image"><img alt="Victoria Cross (Canada) ribbon bar.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Victoria_Cross_(Canada)_ribbon_bar.png/35px-Victoria_Cross_(Canada)_ribbon_bar.png" width="35" height="9" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Victoria_Cross_%28Canada%29_ribbon_bar.png/53px-Victoria_Cross_%28Canada%29_ribbon_bar.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Victoria_Cross_%28Canada%29_ribbon_bar.png/70px-Victoria_Cross_%28Canada%29_ribbon_bar.png 2x" /></a> <strong class="selflink">Victoria Cross (VC)</strong></li>
<li>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png" class="image"><img alt="George Cross UK ribbon.png" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/de/George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png/35px-George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png" width="35" height="11" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/de/George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png/53px-George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/de/George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png/70px-George_Cross_UK_ribbon.png 2x" /></a> <a href="George_Cross" title="George Cross">George Cross (GC)</a></li>
